caption:
Deadline Extended! Don’t miss your chance to be a part of something amazing! No prior experience required🎶
Apply by September 15th through the link in bio!

UTNC is hosting our Trial Classes for the Fall semester on September 18 5-7pm and September 21 10am-12pm!!

If you’re interested in what naginata has to offer but aren’t ready to 100% commit yet, our trial classes give you the opportunity to learn some of the basics, watch some of the more advanced members, and learn what you can gain by joining our community.

We hope to see you guys there - practices are in the Lower Gym in the Hart House Fitness Centre! Just bring yourselves, some comfy clothes, and a water bottle.

Come out to Coronation Park this Sunday, Sept 8 from 2-6 pm for Free Food, Fun Games and kick off the year on the right note!

Fill out the RSVP in our bio to let us know you are coming and what food you want!
Location: 711 Lakeshore Blvd West

As is UTOC tradition, this week we are having an info night for new members!! This is a great opportunity to meet the exec team and all UTOCers 🌲 We will be going over what you can expect this year and general information about the club. After, we will walk over to Christie Pits Park to enjoy a bonfire from 7:00 PM to 8:30 PM. We hope to see you there!! 🔥

🚀 Join the Blueprint Revolution! 🌟

Are you passionate about coding and eager to make a real-world impact? This is your chance to be part of something BIG! 💻✨

We’re on the hunt for dedicated Developers to join our dynamic team, where you’ll be crafting cutting-edge software solutions that matter. As part of our core dev team, you’ll collaborate with talented designers and project leads, bringing innovative ideas to life. Plus, you’ll only need to commit 6-8 hours a week, making it the perfect opportunity to grow your skills while balancing other responsibilities!

🚨 Deadline: Sept 22 — Don’t miss out on this chance to make your mark! Apply now through the link in our bio, at https://bit.ly/bppd2024, or visit our website at http://www.uoftblueprint.org! 🌐

Let’s build something amazing together. 🌍🔧
